scene.message:
Nanjo: What's wrong? Is the{nl}
school gate barricaded?{waitkey}{clearbox}Hurry, or the hospital's{nl}
reception may close on us.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Ugh, Vice Principal{nl}
Hannya's right there!{nl}
Man, I can't stand that guy-{waitkey}{nl}
Let's get outta here quick!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: You know, aside from{nl}
Ms. Saeko and the Principal,{nl}
this school's got no decent{nl}
teachers at all, huh?{waitkey}{ret}

V.P. Hannya: Who said you{nl}
lot could pass through here?{waitkey}{clearbox}If you want out, use the gate{nl}
like proper students! The{nl}
Principal's gone too soft -{waitkey}that's why our school's full{nl}
of little brats like you!{waitkey}{clearbox}Now get moving, the other{nl}
way! I'll have workers fill{nl}
this hole in right away!{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Vice Principal Hannya{nl}
A real stickler - very{nl}
unpopular with the students.{waitkey}{ret}
